title: NOUT Live on KEXP from Trans Musicales. Discover more artists from the international showcase today!

author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Nout performing live at the l’Antipode in Rennes, France, during Trans Musicales 2024. Recorded December 08, 2024.

Songs:
The Last Train
Nuit de Sabbat
Gros Canard
Sauvages

Blanche Lafuente - Drums, Vocals
Rafaelle Rinaudo - Harp
Delphine Joussein - Flute, Vocals

Audio & Mastering Engineer: Matt Ogaz
Guest Audio Engineer: Johann Berger
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Scott Holpainen & Luke Knecht
Editor: Jim Beckmann
